data.description: Move-in Ready! Lovely 4-bedroom ranch designed with espresso cabinets, luxury vinyl plank flooring, stainless steel appliances including a gas range and large island!  Plenty of storage with a walk-in pantry and the primary bedroom includes a walk-in closet. High efficiency A/C , Smart Home Technology Package, tankless hot water heater, full front yard landscaping and a covered back patio included!  Store your toys in the 3 car garage. This home comes with DR Horton's 1/2/10 warranty. DR Horton offers lender incentives through preferred lender DHI Mortgage!
